Package parser.interfaces

Interface Exec

All Superinterfaces:
Validator
All Known Implementing Classes:
BaseNode, ComparatorNode, ElseIfNode, ElseNode, EmptyNode, EqualToNode, EvaluateNode, ForNode, GetVariableNode, GreaterThanNode, IfNode, LessThanNode, MazeActionNode, MethodNode, PrintNode, VariableActionNode, VariableAssignmentNode, VariableNode, WhileNode
public interface Exec
extends Validator
This is used to delineate any classes that are executed instead of evaluated in teh parser. It contains a basic execute method and a method to get the type returned at execution.
